diff_user.user:
An incorrect diff format was detected in this change:
Here's a focused improvement to enhance the sentence fluency and handle multiple triples more effectively by adding conjunctions and relative clauses:

```diff
<<<<<<< SEARCH
            sentence += f"{triple.subject} {triple.predicate} {triple.object}. "
>>>>>>> REPLACE
            if i > 0 and triples[i-1].subject == triple.subject:
                sentence = sentence.rstrip(". ")  # Remove trailing punctuation
                if triple.predicate == "country" and triples[i-1].predicate == "nationality":
                    sentence += f" and is from {triple.object}."
                elif triple.predicate == "language" and triples[i-1].predicate == "country":
                    sentence += f", where {triple.object} is spoken."
                else:
                    sentence += f" and {triple.predicate} {triple.object}."
            else:
                sentence += f"{triple.subject} {triple.predicate} {triple.object}. "
```

Please fix it to the correct format.
